      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个用户旅程图，主题是「添加商品到愿望清单」。整个流程分成两大阶段：进入线上商店和浏览商店。第一阶段用户要先访问网站，然后用我们的FinTech_LedgerService登录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Adding an item to the wishlist",
        "Enter online shop",
        "Visit website",
        "Log in (FinTech_LedgerService)"
